Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:09.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.42,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was a Christmas present!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:17.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to a very common high school boy's, Ayasaki Hayate's, generous parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:22.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he was kindly given to very nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:27.36,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, destiny was waiting for him at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:31.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure, but you saved me. {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Villains! Hand her back to me now! {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:45.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll make him my, Sanzenin Nagi's, new butler! {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:49.31,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:52.03,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who dedicates himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:58.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:00.44,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:08.11,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll make him my, Sanzenin Nagi's, new butler! {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:13.18,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stating it twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.91,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you set?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.69,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, Mr. Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You sound as though I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.47,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,You are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:11.41,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,You were so red that we couldn't even put you on the airwaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But if so, oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:23.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any family to grieve over me, or a house to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.29,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.82,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,A kidnapper trying to act as a tragic hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.47,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Besides in the last episode, although it was in your mind, you did punch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:41.53,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget. Although it didn't actually happen,\Nwhat you tried to do is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.08,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.08,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This splendor... it can't be of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, this is Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:15.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If not, it has to be an illusion created by my mind due to a long, poor life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Santa Claus. I'll enjoy it to my fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid hero we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:28.34,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,He did hit his head hard, but there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:32.22,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been training regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.55,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,If anything comes up, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:43.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Maria. I want to make him Himegami's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm having a hard time following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it's the person who saved my life's wish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.45,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He confessed love to me at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Very passionately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to take you away" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.82,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, when Hayate wakes up, let me know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:03.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:08.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on? I have to check on a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.59,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, my dream's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's more flamboyant than anything I'd ever seen when I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:26.64,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Man, but if this is Heaven, it's not such a bad idea to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The alone part is a little lonely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.52,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I-It does feel good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-It really calms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.99,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:46.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a dream? Wh-Why is that scarf person here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.11,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:47.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:51.53,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is really quite tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:56.37,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Although your life isn't in any danger, to take a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The wounds would open for any normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And the bath is now stained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.90,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's stained by the red bath agent that oozed out of Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.65,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:23.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,No wait, we're not even at the halfway point of the episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:25.83,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a fan service shot to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.39,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Ayasaki Hayate-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the bath-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:41.23,Default-alt,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You've been out all this time, ever since you were carried into the mansion, but are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I've been out all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.46,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.05,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You've been out the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:49.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:56.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but how do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.91,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:06.97,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lady Sanzenin Nagi-sama's mansion, whom you saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.80,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.34,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And I am her maid, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:20.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And, though I know it's impolite of me, I took a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.62,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you are in a difficult position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:31.29,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I have something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.66,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding what happened with our Lady in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everything's exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that you were going to "take her away"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I'll never even think about kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.91,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know how to apologize regarding this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:08:00.07,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are lies that people say out of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were awake already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for being so kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry for the terrible request I made to you at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:19.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For ¥156,804,000, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:24.26,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it surprised me, but I wasn't against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was your first moment being confessed to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Although you mistook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:34.47,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know each other well,\Nso I'm not too sure about rushing the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've given it some thought after that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for live-in work, weren't you? {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.28,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then be my butler here at the mansion. {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:47.32,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:53.90,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Milady, how about asking his situation first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.63,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But we do need a replacement for Himegami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:59.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, your toughness is greater than anyone's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:03.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He was moving even after getting hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:07.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She's about to forgive me for trying to kidnap her and is now offering me live-in work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What a... What a kind little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This must be my first present from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.10,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,No, not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.39,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Hayate-kun doesn't know what a butler does, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:31.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I, Ayasaki Hayate,\Nwill protect Milady, even at the cost of my own life! {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.36,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.40,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such an embarrassing thing in front of Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:45.10,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should we do about these two naturally empty minds? {ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.04,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.54,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A new butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:55.82,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we were looking for a replacement\Nto fill in for head butler with Himegami gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.60,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,but what exactly is this Ayasaki Hayate boy like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.05,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:10.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can catch up to a car speeding at 120km/h\Non a bicycle and can withstand being run over by said car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.59,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, which ***dam is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.71,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,That's as sturdy as a giant robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.97,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, Klaus-san, he is a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.34,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And, that ***dam is not a giant robot, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.94,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, so that ***dam isn't a giant robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:29.23,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying anime to have\Na common interest with Milady, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.90,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,"Foolishness caused by youth."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.52,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be understanding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.35,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,So regarding Hayate-kun's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:40.92,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, the likes of him won't suffice as our butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.21,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Have him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.03,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.26,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,How's the fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:11:00.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. It was worth fixing it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san, you did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.18,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:10.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly is my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.90,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.15,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's the end of the year, I guess cleaning every spot you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:21.81,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san said to send him out, but I cannot really do that, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning... Then I can do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If I get fired from here, I can't pay the ¥156,804,000 back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have a place to live, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today, my new life will start here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as a butler to the Sanzenin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.88,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Time for commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.68,Default,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.92,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today, my new life will start here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,As a butler to the Sanzenin family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I got to say it all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:06.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nagi. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.19,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:14.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san redid these clothes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope you work well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:23.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel she's become cold all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.88,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, I think she's getting heated up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:31.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll gain her trust back through work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:32.70,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:37.63,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,His motivation... How can I send him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And how can I untangle the misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.01,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the right attitude to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That was way too mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If I could sew like Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.19,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.97,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria. Where's Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He's helping me with cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:15.01,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He's filled with motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.29,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he is going to work hard to gain your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you have anything in mind,\NI think it is the best if you talk to him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right! We have to get to know each other well, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:29.96,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.56,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to where Hayate is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.51,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you kindly untangle the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:43.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san, could you check the cleaning for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:50.81,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, just thinking how unsynchronized you two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.26,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really clean here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Does it? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Very thorough in the smallest places.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.51,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:11.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that door handle was made of silver, so I used Silver Duster to polish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:18.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This statue here, after taking the stain off with a brush made of brass, I cleaned with a neutral detergent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:20.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wiped the water off and finished it with a wax coating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:26.17,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The carpet was Kilim style made with wool,\Nso I used cosmetic detergent with cold water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.08,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.64,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm honestly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, I'm at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:39.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was working at a sanitation company when I was eight, while hiding my age, to get money for my parents to drink off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So cleaning turns out to be one of my specialties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:52.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Klaus-san, I can't find a reason to send Hayate-kun off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:56.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Nagi's eye for selecting people seems to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But this mansion is really huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,How many rooms are there to clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Study?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense anyone in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady's notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:29.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A picture diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.83,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I mustn't look at a private thing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:34.87,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at in someone else's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,M-Milady! Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:48.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't read your picture diary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Picture diary, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.40,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.71,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I don't care about you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.17,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What do you understand about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Hayate, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.25,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It was short, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:26.92,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, kiddo. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:28.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.12,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun really left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,On a black pumpkin carriage, too. {Reference to Cinderella. What that carriage called?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.59,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:59.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! The second half of this episode isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to leave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I only told him to get out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd leave the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:13.38,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It is because you are not in the habit of putting away your important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.45,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Not much we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.85,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Let us forget about Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:22.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you are through with him, then there is no reason to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate Hayate-kun, then it is better to leave things as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't hate him or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.35,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.84,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Hayate is the person who saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:40.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,As a part of Sanzenin, I can't abandon my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:49.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mister Nice People, where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.12,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,The Immigration Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.45,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so happy. Volunteer work is waiting for me ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.44,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to return to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.69,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't be able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do? At this rate, my life will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,First, it'll be a cruise with everyone on a gorgeous boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But on the way, pirates will attack us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and for some reason I'll get recruited into their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:17.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,After becoming a wanted man,\NI get cornered by an ocean monkey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:22.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and my dream to become the Pirate King sinks into a cross-shaped ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.26,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I have a little emergency to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:33.47,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Your luxury boat is ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.32,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.79,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.44,Default-alt,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.99,Default-alt,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:53.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That voice. Could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:58.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milad-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.91,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Na-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.07,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mask the Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I came here at the request of Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,And, here's a message from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,"I-I'm sorry for yelling at you earlier."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.25,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she wanted me to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:28.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,A-And, what you saw in the notebook is her latest work,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:32.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,a manga titled {\i1}Millennium Legend: Magical Destroy{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,and it absolutely wasn't a picture diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mask the Money-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:43.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Then continue being a butler at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be happy that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.65,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're not going to be able to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:56.58,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a ¥156,804,000 debt made by his parents to pay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.40,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to return it in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.26,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.24,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So what about this piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:04.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up, or did you not hear me, baldy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.32,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,This brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't touch this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.58,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:25.78,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want us to touch her,\Nthen pay the ¥156,804,000 back right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The entire debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:36.93,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.44,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,That's all real money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.26,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any more problems now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.49,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.16,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:57.33,Default,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Now you need to get the money back from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Mask the Money-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When you see Milady, please relay a message for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I will pay the money back with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for my position as butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:16.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But she meant the money as a gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I have to pay it off! Otherwise I can't be even with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:23.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she came to save me with such a funny looking mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have to note that she thought it was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:27.87,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So that money-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Pay it off!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:34.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, money-related matters must be kept black and white for the sake of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:41.45,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So you must work like a horse to pay everything back to Sanzenin Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:47.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely, DEFINITELY, not going to give you any discounts, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:48.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Mask the Money-san, your mask fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.35,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.86,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,They are like brother and sister.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.17,0:22:04.80,Default-alt,PLACEHOLDER,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.04,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.66,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't look!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.99,0:21:58.86,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.45,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.63,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.13,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.80,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.15,0:22:04.80,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:13.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And this is how the two's Christmas came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, spring is still far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:16.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,One trouble after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:24.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, we'll pit the mascot character of this anime and 21st-century household machines in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:07.77,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely against hiring a boy who's so pathetic and looks like he'll never have any luck with money for the rest of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:08.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:14.12,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you see a problem with Hayate-kun's strength or potential, how about testing him?
